{"tid":918001,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"當年有個中學同學成日笑人唔努力讀書入大學，幾年後比人笑番轉頭","createTime":"2018-11-27T00:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T16:05:25.000Z","uid":9683,"like":5,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6050d7858e630c196ab5b072a973d4e5d2e1c732","tid":918001,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T00:49:13.000Z","msg":"話說今日發現左個中學同學由做工程轉左做地產，成件事原本都冇咩問題，問題在於佢中學個時成日宣傳入唔到大學就係垃圾依d 老土思想，話咩唔入大學就冇前途等等。<br />\n<br />\n公開試之後，佢的確入到大學，仲搵到份同既個科相關既工作，但最後結果撈唔掂轉做地產，今日比我地成班中學同學係wtsgp 笑佢讀完大學無撚用，浪費時間同錢，不如早d 出黎做野好過。<br />\n<br />\n利伸，degree holder"},{"pid":"07373049c2f68cc1c696dfd2c79eae9e8bf41da0","tid":918001,"uid":21423,"like":91,"dislike":15,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb74cf81c92469519976723b8cc75b90335ae6f7","tid":918001,"uid":38604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T00:52:32.000Z","msg":"I大世界第一"},{"pid":"297faa75be10c3cde9b5e366e5513995bca7497f","tid":918001,"uid":209270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"👌🏻👌🏻"},{"pid":"b0720822ed4c433307eba7580abb1b46e3d83e4c","tid":918001,"uid":9683,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"quote":{"pid":"07373049c2f68cc1c696dfd2c79eae9e8bf41da0","tid":918001,"uid":21423,"like":91,"dislike":15,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母，係咁追擊我做乜9阿，臭西</span></span>"},{"pid":"0dfbeb7112272b9698092975f2ad1f883e67ab42","tid":918001,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bb74cf81c92469519976723b8cc75b90335ae6f7","tid":918001,"uid":38604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T00:52:32.000Z","msg":"I大世界第一"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T00:53:49.000Z","msg":"i 大都係垃圾"},{"pid":"6610ee0e1801b2099f814a589fb6de58d8aa7fe9","tid":918001,"uid":92376,"l