左滿足自己自卑心理而以讀唔到大學黎打飛機就好有問題<br />\n<br />\n得, 入大學最垃圾, 入唔到大學就最撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112d882a68fea284b0bd3c1d484ce0f39eb935ff","tid":918001,"uid":112551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"呢個世界居然係唔努力讀書的人笑努力的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，文革年代？讀書只係為錢就真係可憐<br />\n<br />\n利伸： 私樓仔。"},{"pid":"354c469c317c4ad6347dcbc18836950c2159cb08","tid":918001,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"112d882a68fea284b0bd3c1d484ce0f39eb935ff","tid":918001,"uid":112551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"呢個世界居然係唔努力讀書的人笑努力的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，文革年代？讀書只係為錢就真係可憐<br />\n<br />\n利伸： 私樓仔。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"贏撚晒啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe3d845b991897ccb0ba412e08e6a8d2100be1e","tid":918001,"uid":199016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:05:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}